name: Double Helix in Diamond Spaceship
description:
In the post human world, skull strapped with MR goggles on the ground.
Snowy, only a floating diamond spaceship in the air.
Among the rising bubbles, a twinkling pair of DNA double helix from the mankind is reserved.
This is the end of the world, or is it only a new beginning?
The skull is witnessing...

// The artwork is created in 3D virtual reality.
